# Constraints

## Boundaries

- This repository documentation should remain safe to publish internally or externally as needed.
- Sensitive operational details should be omitted or abstracted.
- The documentation structure should guide readers without duplicating every implementation detail.

## Non-Goals

- document every code path in detail
- expose private production intelligence
- replace architecture decisions with vague narrative

## Maintenance Rule

When project direction changes, update the highest-level documents first.
